<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink364">
<l>muḷavumā valci yeyiṉar taṅkai</l>
<l>yiḷamā veyiṟṟikku minnilai yaṟiyac</l>
<l>colliṉē ṉirakku maḷavai</l>
<l>veṉvēl viṭalai viraiyā tīmē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>Until I spoke and pleaded [for you], </l>
<l>so that the young dark eyiṉar woman also knew about this situation, </l>
<l>o warrior with victorious spear, </l>
<l>do not act in haste! </l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
